{"word":"κατακλύζω","slug":"κατακλύζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατακλύζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-κλύσω</el>) (<a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <el>-κλύσσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to dash over, flood, deluge, inundate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to deluge, overwhelm</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>κύματι κατακλυσθῆν</el> (aor1 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <el>-κλυσθῆναι</el>), <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to wash down</i> or <i>away</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to wash out, wash away</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}